# The `DbgEntity` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This class is defined as the common parent of <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbgvariable">DbgVariable</a> and <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbglabel">DbgLabel</a> such that it could levarage polymorphism to extract common code for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbgvariable">DbgVariable</a> and <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbglabel">DbgLabel</a>. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

This class is defined as the common parent of <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbgvariable">DbgVariable</a> and <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbglabel">DbgLabel</a> such that it could levarage polymorphism to extract common code for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbgvariable">DbgVariable</a> and <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbglabel">DbgLabel</a>.
